item.title: CVE-2023-1623|2023-04-24T18:31:01.462Z -- unknown -- custom%20post%20type%20ui
item.description: The Custom Post Type UI WordPress plugin before 1.13.5 does not properly check for CSRF when sending the debug information to a user supplied email, which could allow attackers to make a logged in admin send such information to an arbitrary email address via a CSRF attack.
